reviewText: As an avid user of the "old" THE FIRM workouts, this was my first "Kick Butt!" and my first experience working out with Keli Roberts.  What a treat!  I like the work of the weights, the relaxing nature of the workout, and just the way she says "strong!"  I have a large collection of workouts and this is still one of my faves for working with medium/heavy weights.
Not what I expected..thought it was as a new Kell Roberts workout.
